## ⛳ Completion signal — REQUIRED LAST LINE (run_claude_job.sh reads this for Steve's Telegram alert)

After all other work and logging, the VERY LAST line of your output MUST be exactly one of:
- `ROUTINE_COMPLETE` — every step finished (both librarian dispatches + all hygiene steps), nothing skipped/blocked/partial.
- `ROUTINE_INCOMPLETE: <one-line reason>` — anything was skipped, blocked, deferred, or failed (including a failed/blocked librarian dispatch).

Output nothing after that line. This line is how Steve gets a done / not-fully-done alert on Telegram.
